A very rare office sighing for Big Carpe. So when I step out, I gotta get right! Big fellas, I know nowadays I wear custom suits but that’s not where I started. Some of my first suits in HS were from Value City. We then graduated to Macy’s. During undergrad and after my spot was @kgfashion . Those 3 suits for $200 specials did numbers! I say all this to say, you don’t have to break the bank to be fly. Be resourceful. 💯💯

Versatility is key 🔑 

I take pride in being able to dress for any occasion. I developed my personal style through magazines, blogs, traveling, and the internet. With social media we can see fits from all over the globe for inspiration. 

Big fellas reach out to me stating that they are motivated to put effort into their appearance by seeing my posts. That motivates me to stay consistent because I know the content is resonating. 

Keep an open mind about style, be a sponge and don’t box yourself in. I love seeing the fits y’all put together. Continue to tag and send me the drip. 🙏🏼💪🏼🌊
